content: A devastating day for our country. For me a day when professional and personal collide. A very painful day as the daughter of a former US Congressman... You watch your mother or father go to Washington to serve the people...  make sacrifices and try to do the right thing. It's a thankless job at times... and yet it can be the most rewarding and fulfilling.  My heart aches for our members of Congress today on both sides of the aisle. I pray for Majority Whip Scalise and Rep. Williams and their families, Special Agent Griner and Bailey of the US Capitol Police. The USCP remain part of our family.  Mr. Barth and Mr. Mika.  This is one of my favorite photos of my father and his dear dear friend and colleague California Republican Rep. Jerry Lewis.  They respected, admired, and worked well together. The reference to Sosa and McGuire seems fitting as tomorrow night the bipartisan Congressional Baseball Game will go on... raising money for the Boys and Girls Club of Greater Washington. They don't see red or blue...   they just see good guys working together. That's the way it should be.
name: Lori Stokes

content:
I know a month has gone by... but I think it's just now registering! I have a college graduate! So I just want to say to my Nikki... From watching you walk into Miss MaryAnn's pre-school class... to watching you glide across the stage of Georgetown University to get your diploma I have always told you, you will change the world. It's not just that your brilliant, determined and focused... but you have a consciense.  You've never thought the world owed you anything... you've always understood you have to work hard to achieve your goals. Already at 22 you have founded and implemented an organization to include and elevate others. You have positioned yourself to follow your dream... that's happening now with the NBA. Like your grandfather, you know there is no wrong if you live your life right. Like all parents... I've tried to give you the best foundation to make your life choices. You're already proving through your journey you'll enrich the lives of others. I'm so proud of you! 
Now go out and change the world!!
